snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate - Mii Fighter Costumes #7 - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
A selection of Creeper, Pig, Diamond Armor, Gil, Bomberman, and Travis Mii Fighter costumes are arriving as paid DLC in Super Smash Bros. Ultimate!
